      <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> We collect information about how you interact with our website to improve your experience. This may include IP addresses, browser types, and pages visited.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>We use the information collected to:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Authenticate Users:</strong> Provide secure login through Google or via the password you set.</li>
      <li><strong>Enhance User Experience:</strong> Personalize your experience and respond to your inquiries or support needs.</li>
      <li><strong>Improve Our Services:</strong> Analyze usage patterns to enhance our website’s performance and features.</li>
      <li><strong>Communicate:</strong> Send you updates, notifications, and promotional materials related to our services, if you have opted to receive them.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">3. Data Security</h2>
    <p>We prioritize the security of your data:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Authentication:</strong> We utilize Google’s OAuth 2.0 for secure authentication, ensuring your Google credentials are not stored or handled by us.</li>
      <li><strong>Password Protection:</strong> Passwords created on our site are encrypted using industry-standard hashing algorithms. We employ robust security measures to protect against unauthorized access.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <h2 class="section-title">4. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties except in the following cases:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>With Your Consent:</strong> If you agree to share your information with third parties.</li>
      <li><strong>Service Providers:</strong> We may use third-party services to help us operate our website and provide services to you, but they are bound by confidentiality agreements.</li>
      <li><strong>Legal Requirements:</strong> We may disclose your information to comply with legal obligations or protect our rights and safety.</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

